text: Mai El Kamash (; born 10 September 1994) is an Egyptian tennis player. El Kamash has a WTA singles career high ranking of 913 achieved on 15 July 2013. She also has a WTA doubles career high ranking of 876 achieved on 7 October 2013. El Kamash has won one ITF doubles titles.
